<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .code-container {
            background-color: #e9e9e9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Email Verification</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Hey {{ name }},</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up! Please use the verification code below to confirm your email address:</p>
        <div class="code-container">
            <strong>{{ verificationCode }}</strong>
        </div>
        <p>Enter this code in the Offlinery app to complete your email verification.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>